headline: Abbott Declares 405th Consecutive Quarterly Dividend
summary: ABBOTT PARK, Ill. - The board of directors of Abbott today declared a quarterly common dividend of 59 cents per share.This marks the 405th consecutive quarterly dividend to be paid by Abbott since...
